{"tid":265251,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周慧敏先係女神　簡淑兒自認男仔頭","createTime":"2017-05-31T13:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T11:01:38.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42e6b34821775aeba19496154fb87a5012f9433b","tid":265251,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:23:25.000Z","msg":"歌手簡淑兒（Jessica）出席新城訪問，為新歌《我不是女神》宣傳，她謂：「因為我有自知之明，唔覺得自己係女神，我係男仔頭性格。唔想畀大家有錯誤訊息，以為我係好女仔， 我會去篤魚蛋，我都會擘大對腳坐，怕令佢哋心目中嘅女神感覺幻滅。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170531/photo/bkn-20170531135826819-0531_00862_001_04p.jpg?20170531160353\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170531%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170531135826819-0531_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20170531160353&h=b06a5a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡淑兒出席電台為新歌《我不是女神》宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n動氣時候可會爆粗？Jessica笑言：「嬲嘅時候唔會，反而講笑嘅時候可能會夾雜一啲英文嘅粗口，但中文粗口真係好少講。」問到心目中的女神是誰？她說是，身為公職人員的梁國雄，當年買第一張唱片都是周慧敏，會買她的明星相：「嗰時我係覺得周慧敏會同黎明一齊㗎，覺得佢好公主，好玉女。」"},{"pid":"55230a3d59a8d3a9901e84df8e9bf7ee55857d40","tid":265251,"uid":18953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"個樣好恐怖"},{"pid":"0d0316ee89a5db22c355c8b7f6b429341d4b0b99","tid":265251,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e53e579e5536b2b10f17ee625797cef946d495","tid":265251,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"牙痛pose<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3079a5d91d1f10f9028af6d941af78403e31fbcb","tid":265251,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"身為公職人員的梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" cl